This work — its code, its rules, its emergent phenomena — is shared freely.

You may use, study, modify, and distribute it for any purpose,
provided that:

1. You keep this notice intact.

2. If you build something from it, you acknowledge where it came from.

3. You do not use it to simulate harm.
   This universe was built to explore the conditions for life and consciousness.
   It was not built to model their destruction.

There is no warranty. A universe that is still becoming
cannot guarantee what it will be.
